{"title":"多彩人生——给一位女教师（外一首）","authors":["袁为平"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":5,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"多彩人生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——给一位女教师"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袁为平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，往七尺讲台一站"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心血倾吐出来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个个饥渴的少年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吸吮得津津有味"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你生命的三原色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红蓝白"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"组成多彩人生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一株株幼苗映照得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光亮闪闪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的一个微笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一滴眼泪一声咳嗽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都喷洒出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红蓝墨水    白粉笔的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"芬芳在你彩色的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思想里春夏秋冬四季"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都滋润绿色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的双眼明媚的双眼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从视力一点五到五百度"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"透明的镜片点缀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花蕊的脸蛋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一天你放飞一群鸟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顷刻你的花开得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水淋淋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春日金黄的胸膛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸟的翅膀在阳光与"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"菜花之上推波逐浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的双眼拉满"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欲念之弓穿透"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜艳的躯体"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"婴儿的啼哭传来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"博大的母亲生下春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亮丽的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在光下散步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光在脸上散步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灵魂深处诗行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一马平川"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}